high_descs: pick up the egg sitting on the table beside the spatula
take the egg and go to the fridge
open the door and set the egg on the top shelf close the door and then open it and take out the egg
take the egg and go to the microwave across the room
open the microwave and set the egg inside
anns.task_desc: put the egg in the microwave

high_descs: Move to the other side of the round black table on your left.
Pick up the egg on the table.
Turn around, bring the egg to the fridge.
Chill the egg in the fridge.
Bring the chilled egg to microwave, across the room to the right of the fridge, on the counter.
Put the egg in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled egg in the microwave.

high_descs: Walk forward and turn around to the left to the left to face the kitchen table.
Pick up the egg on the kitchen table.
Turn around and step forward to face the fridge.
Cool the egg in the fridge and remove it.
Turn right and cross the room to face the microwave.
Place the egg in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: To cool an egg and place it in the microwave.
